AB  - When does an individual's expected wealth accumulation profile increase as earnings risk increases? This paper answers this question for multi-period models where earnings shocks are independent over time. Sufficient conditions are stated in terms of properties of a decision rule for savings and, alternatively, in terms of properties of preferences.
Y2  - 3/25/2024
UR  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1467-937X.2004.00303.x
